Name: FUEL HOLDINGS RATING
Explanation: USED TO EXPRESS THE CURRENT FUEL HOLDINGS AS A PERCENTAGE OF THE TOTAL POSSIBLE FUEL HOLDINGS.

Name: MANPOWER FATIGUE RATING
Explanation: THE RELATIVE FATIGUE CONDITION OF PERSONNEL OR A UNIT.

Name: PERSONNEL STRENGTH RATING
Explanation: USED TO EXPRESS A UNITS AVAILABLE PERSONNEL STRENGTH AS A PERCENTAGE OF ITS WARTIME STRENGTH.

Name: MAJOR EQUIPMENTS AVAILABLE RATING
Explanation: USED TO EXPRESS THE AVAILABLE MAJOR EQUIPMENT AS A PERCENTAGE OF ITS WARTIME AUTHORIZED QUANTITY.

Name: AMMUNITION HOLDINGS RATING
Explanation: USED TO EXPRESS THE CURRENT AMMUNITION HOLDINGS AS A PERCENTAGE OF UNIT BASIC LOAD.
